The road between Tekwane South and eNtokozweni leading to KaNyamazane should be avoided after a bridge on the road collapsed last night.  READ: Sinkhole finally causes bridge to collapse – as locals warned Ward councillor Joseph Mashaba urged motorists and pedestrians to avoid using this road.  Earlier this week Tekwane South and eNtokozweni community members took to the streets, calling for the City of Mbombela to repair the sinkhole. *This is a developing story: We’ll give updates on the situation as we learn more.